rows.label: tev065701_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Go Rogan about Wrothian duty.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Go Rogan about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Go Rogan about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG0001
rows.name:
We Wrothians draw our blades and battle our
adversaries to fulfill our duty to Prince Jiarg.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG0002
rows.name:
But what of you BLADEs? What is your reason for
risking your life to fight the Ganglion?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG0003
rows.name:
...It depends on the person, you say?
Some fight for the future of humanity, while others
complete missions for selfish gain?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG0004
rows.name:
Then you are willing to put your life on the line without
knowing if the person next to you is of the same mind?
Without so much as a common cause?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG0005
rows.name:
Perhaps that free-spirited approach is why you are able
to stand up to the Ganglion, whereas we were not.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG0010
rows.name:
I am Go Rogan, commander of the Wrothian
Mercenaries, Third Company.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG0011
rows.name:
Of course, said company is just a ragtag bunch of
novices scrounged together by necessity after our
alliance with you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG0012
rows.name:
But with training—and train we shall—my company will
be every bit as strong as the Hundred Hellions![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG0013
rows.name: May we meet again on some future battlefield.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG0018
rows.name:
Gi Zang has grown a shoulder or two since last I
saw him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG0019
rows.name:
He will make a good rival. And I have you to thank
for growing as strong as I![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG0020
rows.name:
Let me thank you on behalf of my departed brothers
of the Hundred Hellions.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG0021
rows.name:
If Gi Zang passes this skill and strength on to the other
Wrothian warriors...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG0022
rows.name:
then we may yet see a force equal to the Hundred
Hellions![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG1001
rows.name:
Before the Ganglion came to our homeworld,
the Wrothian army had an elite covert force called the
Hundred Hellions.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG1002
rows.name:
Despite their small numbers, the Hellions were combat
elites—legends that other soldiers would speak of only
in awestruck tones.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG1003
rows.name:
They resisted the Ganglion to the very end,
and it cost nearly all of their lives.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG1004
rows.name:
Gi Zang alone survived among all the Hellions,
and he came here to Mira with the rest of us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG1005
rows.name:
He has since left our ranks—to train, he said.
I wonder how he fares?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_JNK1010
rows.name: Reassure[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_SEL1011
rows.name: Tell Go Rogan about Gi Zang.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_JNK1020
rows.name: Relate[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_SEL1021
rows.name:
Tell Go Rogan that the Hundred
Hellions sound fascinating.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG1006
rows.name: What? You know him?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG1007
rows.name: ...I see. So he has grown that strong already.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG1008
rows.name:
In that case, he should end his quest and return to us.
We need such strength now![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG1009
rows.name:
They were brave and proud beyond all measure!
Not a Wrothian draws breath who does not look upon
the Hellions with admiration.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065701_MSG1010
rows.name:
Gi Zang wanted to count himself among the best
of them, which is why he continues his reckless quest
to this day, I imagine.[ST:wait ]
